data.description: Welcome home!!! This HUGE 3/4 acre fenced lot with NO HOA is a must see. This gorgeous 5 bedroom brick front Colonial (1 NTC in basement), 4 bathroom, (3 full and 1 half bath) home is move in ready! Rare opportunity in Longwood Estates to be this close to everything yet still your own private oasis. All new luxury plank flooring installed 2021. Main level has a separate living/kids playroom, dining and family room. Large eat in kitchen with all white appliances. Dishwasher just installed 2024. Right off of the kitchen is your light-filled breakfast nook that leads out to your double deck with a fully fenced back yard (new 2021 and does include an additional electric fence) that is perfect for entertaining or just relaxing in the evening with the family. Spacious family room with bay windows and a wood fireplace. Upstairs is your master suite which has a walk in closet and the additional 2nd bedroom attached can be used as an office/nursery. Master bath has double sinks, a soaking tub and a separate shower. Two additional nice size bedrooms with a full bath are also on this level. Head down to the lower level to your additional living space that would make for a fabulous mother in law suite that was just updated in 2021. Mini kitchen with wet bar that includes a refrigerator (mini under sink conveys) quartz countertops, shelves and plenty of storage. Separate entrance outside and a custom built patio. New full bathroom and your 5th bedroom (NTC) that includes a HUGE closet. Garage is fully finished that includes an additional refrigerator, mounted TV, portable heater/ac/dehumidifier, additional shelves and cabinets. Garage floor has a protected rubber flooring. Convenient location to everything! Just minutes from 95/Commuter lots, shopping, dining, parks and more!
